<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>Welcome to NBJ Academy</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Coach Nalloy</h2>
        <p>
            Francysnalloy Amorim Loiola, known as Coach Nalloy, is a Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu black belt, educator, and family man. 
            Originally from Brazil, he brings the authentic essence of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu, combining technical excellence with 
            discipline, respect, and purpose.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Coaching Experience</h2>
        <ul class="experience-list">
            <li>Over 15 years of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu experience</li>
            <li>Black belt for more than 5 years</li>
            <li>Extensive experience coaching children and adults</li>
            <li>Proven experience working with students with special needs, including Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD) and ADHD, using adaptive teaching methods</li>
            <li>Strong focus on confidence, discipline, inclusion, and personal development</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="philosophy">
            Coach Nalloy believes Jiu-Jitsu is not only about technique, but about creating an inclusive environment 
            where every student can grow at their own pace.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>NBJ Academy – A Family Project</h2>
        <p>
            Founded in 2022, NBJ Academy began as an online educational platform. 
            On June 11, 2025, it evolved into a physical academy built on strong family values. 
            Led by Nalloy and his wife Fernanda, NBJ Academy is a family-driven project committed to creating a welcoming, 
            safe, and positive environment for the entire community.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Why Choose NBJ Academy</h2>
        <p>NBJ Academy offers a unique training experience that combines professionalism with a warm, family-focused atmosphere:</p>
        <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li>A family-oriented, light, and enjoyable environment, bringing positivity to the mats while maintaining respect, discipline, and structure</li>
            <li>High-quality instruction with personal attention and inclusive coaching methods</li>
            <li>A strong sense of community where students feel supported and valued</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Comfort & Facilities</h2>
        <ul class="facilities-list">
            <li>Comfortable and well-structured training space</li>
            <li>A dedicated waiting lounge with sofas beside the mats, allowing parents and family members to watch classes comfortably</li>
            <li>A coffee and refreshment station, with coffee, tea, and light snacks available</li>
            <li>A welcoming, calm, and family-friendly atmosphere</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Family Support Spaces</h2>
        <ul class="facilities-list">
            <li>A dedicated children's room available while parents or siblings are training</li>
            <li>Equipped with TV, educational toys, books, air conditioning, and comfortable seating</li>
            <li>Designed to provide a safe and engaging environment for children</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="section-icon">&#129355;</div>
        <h2>Additional Benefits</h2>
        <p>
            Access to a downstairs strength and conditioning gym, with exclusive discounts for NBJ Academy students
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
        <h2>Start Your Journey Today</h2>
        <p>
